IL-18 can promote fibroblast proliferation as well.533 Meanwhile, IL-17A strengthens the neutrophil responses by CXCL1/2/8 and aggravates tissue injury by synthesizing reactive oxygen species (ROS).534 The IL-17A signaling increases the TGFβ1 receptors on fibroblasts and facilitates the secretion of ECM. The adaptive
immune CD4+ Th2 cell can directly activate fibroblasts via IL-4 and
